opam-version: "2.0"
name: "vchan"
version: "2.0.2"
synopsis: "Xen Vchan implementation"
description: """
Vchan is a high performance inter-domain communications protocol using
shared memory. This implementation runs in both userspace and
kernelspace using Mirage."""
